  <entry>
    <title>php入门</title>
    <link href="http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/11/14/php%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/"/>
    <id>http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/11/14/php%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/</id>
    <published>2021-11-14T15:05:47.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-18T12:29:37.661Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PHP代码标记"><a href="#PHP代码标记" class="headerlink" title="PHP代码标记"></a>PHP代码标记</h1><ul><li>ASP标记：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">php代码</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>短标记：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?</span><br><span class="line">Php代码</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>以上两种基本弃用，如需使用，应在配置文件中开启。</li><li>脚本标记：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script language=&quot;php&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">php代码</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>标准标记：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">php代码</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>以上四种标记中，标准标记较为常用。</li></ul><h1 id="PHP注释"><a href="#PHP注释" class="headerlink" title="PHP注释"></a>PHP注释</h1><p>PHP注释有利于初学者学习PHP代码，增加代码可读性。<br>因为PHP代码的底层逻辑是C语言，所以有较多地方与C语言类似。</p><ul><li>行注释（只对一行注释）：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//:后面跟的都是注释</span><br><span class="line"> #:后面跟的都是注释</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>块注释（对多行注释）：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*：</span><br><span class="line">注释内容</span><br><span class="line">*/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="PHP分隔符"><a href="#PHP分隔符" class="headerlink" title="PHP分隔符"></a>PHP分隔符</h1><p>与C语言相同，同样使用“;”来分隔代码行与代码行。</p><h1 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h1><ul><li>定义变量：<br>$字符;  或者  $字符 = 字符或者数字;<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//定义变量：PHP中不需要任何关键字定义变量（赋值）</span><br><span class="line">$var1;      //定义</span><br><span class="line">$var2 = 1;  //定义同时赋值</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>访问变量（输出变量）：<br>echo $字符;<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo $var2; //通过var2变量名字找到存储的内容1，然后输出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>修改变量：<br>$字符 = 其他字符或者数字;<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$var2 = 2;</span><br><span class="line">echo &#x27;&lt;hr/&gt;&#x27;,$var2;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>删除变量：<br>使用unset(变量名字)<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unset($var2);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>预定义变量<br>预定义变量：提前定义的变量，系统定义的变量，存储许多需要用到的数据（预定义变量都是数组）<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$_GET：获取所有表单以get 方式提交的数据；</span><br><span class="line">$_POST：POST提交的数据都会保存在此；</span><br><span class="line">S_REQUEST：GET和POST提交的都会保存</span><br><span class="line">SGLOBALS: PHP中所有的全局变量；</span><br><span class="line">$_SERVER：服务器信息；</span><br><span class="line">$_ SESSION：session会话数据；</span><br><span class="line">$_COOKIE: cookie会话数据；</span><br><span class="line">S_ENV：环境信息；</span><br><span class="line">＄_FILES：用户上传的文件信息。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>变量传递<br>将一个变量赋值给另外一个变量：变量传值。</li></ul><p>变量传值一共有两种方式：值传递，引用传递。<br>值传递：将变量保存的值赋值一份，然后将新的億给另外一个变量保存(两个变量没有关系）<br>引用传递：将变量保存的值所在的内存地址，传递给另外一个变量：两个变量指向同一块内存空间（两个变量是同一个值)<br>引用传递的格式：$新变量 = &amp;$老变量</p><ul><li><ul><li>值传递例子<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">    $a = 1;</span><br><span class="line">$b = $a;//值传递</span><br><span class="line">    $b = 2;</span><br><span class="line">echo $a,$b;//1,2</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><ul><li>引用传递例子<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">    $a = 1;</span><br><span class="line">$b = &amp;$a;//引用传递</span><br><span class="line">$b = 2;</span><br><span class="line">echo $a,$b;//2,2</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
