  <entry>
    <title>其他控制语句</title>
    <link href="http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/10/29/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5/"/>
    <id>http://顾绿绿のblog.com/2021/10/29/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5/</id>
    <published>2021-10-29T11:05:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-12T17:24:15.795Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="break语句"><a href="#break语句" class="headerlink" title="break语句"></a>break语句</h1><ul><li><p>语法格式：<br>  <code>break;</code><br>注：break语句只能在循环语句和switch语句中使用，但当break语句出现在循环体中的switch语句内时，其作用只是跳出switch语句，而不能终止循环的执行。</p></li><li><p>例子：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int a,b;</span><br><span class="line">char c;</span><br><span class="line">do&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     scanf(&quot;%d%c%d&quot;,&amp;a,&amp;c,&amp;b);</span><br><span class="line"> switch(c)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    case &#x27;+&#x27;:printf(&quot;=%d\n&quot;,a+b);break;</span><br><span class="line">case &#x27;-&#x27;:printf(&quot;=%d\n&quot;,a-b);break;</span><br><span class="line">case &#x27;*&#x27;:printf(&quot;=%d\n&quot;,a*b);break;</span><br><span class="line">case &#x27;/&#x27;:if(b!=0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    printf(&quot;=%d\n&quot;,a/b);break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">default:printf(&quot;错误的算式！\n&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;退出程序吗？(Yes/No):&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">getchar()</span><br><span class="line">scanf(&quot;%c&quot;,&amp;c);</span><br><span class="line">  if(c==&#x27;Yes&#x27;||c==&#x27;No&#x27;) break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;while(1);</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个程序中，switch循环语句中的break语句只跳出了switch语句的循环而没有结束程序。想要结束程序得使用后续if语句的break语句。</p></li></ul><h1 id="continue语句"><a href="#continue语句" class="headerlink" title="continue语句"></a>continue语句</h1><p>continue语句只能在循环体中使用，一般配合if语句使用。</p><ul><li>功能<br>结束本次循环，不再进行后续语句，直接开始下一次的循环。</li><li>使用的结构框架<br>for循环结构：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for(表达式1;表达式2;表达式3)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    语句组1</span><br><span class="line">continue;</span><br><span class="line">语句组2</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>while循环框架：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while(表达式2)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    语句组1</span><br><span class="line">continue;</span><br><span class="line">语句组2</span><br><span class="line">表达式3;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="goto语句"><a href="#goto语句" class="headerlink" title="goto语句"></a>goto语句</h1><ul><li><p>语法格式<br><code>goto 语句标号;</code></p></li><li><p>功能<br>无条件回到该语句标号的步骤并且执行后续程序。</p></li><li><p>例子</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int i=1,sum=0;</span><br><span class="line">loop: sum+=i++;</span><br><span class="line">if(i&lt;=100) goto loop;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;1到100的和为：%d\n&quot;,sum);</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h1><p>三种形式的控制语句都有各自严格的形式框架，合理运用可增加程序可读性，但是不一定方便，所以应该根据具体情境进行运用。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;break语句&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#break语句&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;break语句&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;break语句&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;语法格式：&lt;br&gt;  &lt;code&gt;break;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;注：break</summary>
      
    
    
    
